  <description><![CDATA[<p>The five-star Premium L'Hévana residence is located in the heart of <a data-udi="umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88}" title="Meribel">Méribel</a> Centre, a resort renowned for its elegance and traditional feel.</p>
<h2>Central location</h2>
<p><span class="js-toggle-target u-Hidden js-toggle--visible"><span>Residence L’Hevana is located in the centre of Méribel, with the resort facilities and ski lifts accessible by a pedestrian footbridge, making it incredibly easy to get onto the slopes. Spend a day exploring the <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">Three Valleys Ski Area</a>, one of the world’s largest ski areas, with over 600 kilometres on your doorstep. When you have finished skiing for the day, relax in your apartment where you can whip up delicious meals or enjoy après at one of the lively bars. </span></span></p>
<h2>Premium apartments</h2>
<p>The residence have been furnished to a high standard, blending traditional and modern Alpine décor to create a warm and welcoming space. The apartments have a balcony or terrace, so you can marvel at the picturesque mountain views from the comfort of the apartment. The apartments have a dining area and lounge, as well as a well equipped kitchen with all the amenities needed for a self catered stay in the mountains.  Whether you want to cook your own meals or head out for dinner, the supermarket and restaurants are only a short walk away from the residences. Alternatively we have partnered with <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/special-offers/huski-food-drink-delivery-service">Huski</a> who deliver oven-ready meals to your apartments. Choose from a variety of packages to best suit your needs and relax in the evenings, knowing your meals are taken care of. </p>
<h2>Unwind and relax</h2>
<p>After a day of exploring <span>Méribel</span> and the Three Valleys, make the most of the residence's spa and wellness area. Have a dip in the heated indoor swimming pool or soak away any aches and pains in the whirlpool, there is also a steam room and sauna to sooth your senses.  Fully revitalise at the Deep Nature Spa which has a variety of treatments and massages available for you to book locally.</p>
<p>Enjoy a drink at the residence's cocktail bar which occasionally has live music. Alternatively, the property is centrally located in the traditionally charming Méribel, allowing guests to venture to local restaurants, bars and shops. </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
