  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>One bedroom apartments</strong> sleep two to four people and are around 41m². The apartments have a twin bedroom and a living room with double sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom apartments with mountain views</strong> sleep three to six people and are 61m². The apartments have one twin bedroom, one double bedroom and a living room with double sofa bed.</p>
<p>Beds are made on arrival apart from sofa beds and end of stay cleaning is included except the kitchen area. One linen set with towels and bedding is provided per person, per week.</p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Balcony or terrace</li>
<li>Living area</li>
<li>Twin or double beds (please specify preference when booking)</li>
<li>Bath with shower head attachment or shower room</li>
<li>Heated towel rails</li>
<li>WC</li>
<li>Open plan dining area</li>
<li>Kitchenette equipped with stove tops, microwave, oven, dish washer, fridge, kettle</li>
<li>Toaster</li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Cleaning kit</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Hair dryer</li>
<li>Bed linen and towels</li>
<li>Safe (on request)</li>
<li>Two bathrobes per apartment</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
